Curvature: HTML5 Canvas Curves Generator/Tool

Curvature is a tool lets you design curves using Canvas 2d APIs!

Curvature lets you draw unlimited Bezier curves and also generates exact code for you!


Try the tool:
http://bit.ly/curvature-tool

Get source code:
http://bit.ly/curvature-source

Here is a video that may help you understand the tool: 
